reviews.text: 味道非常好，份量正常，價錢合理，酒吧氣氛，但要留意入座時間
主打豬手，其他食物也不錯，環境不會像其他酒吧般嘈雜，適合三五知己聚頭。

A nice German restaurant with reasonable price.  Choices are limited.  Sausage platter has been localized and a bit salty with the source.  Pork knuckle was fine.  Will visit again.
